<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521914' id='t-521914'>My brain's making amyloid-beta right now,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='523772' id='t-523772'>and so is yours.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='525930' id='t-525930'>But in patients with Alzheimer's disease,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='527932' id='t-527932'>amyloid-beta builds up and aggregates</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='530531' id='t-530531'>in the spaces between the brain's cells,</span>
