</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='557705' id='t-557705'>So if sleep, then,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='559384' id='t-559384'>is part of the brain's solution</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561342' id='t-561342'>to the problem of waste clearance,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='563352' id='t-563352'>then this may dramatically change how we think</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='565728' id='t-565728'>about the relationship between sleep,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='567963' id='t-567963'>amyloid-beta, and Alzheimer's disease.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='571319' id='t-571319'>A series of recent clinical studies</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573277' id='t-573277'>suggest that among patients</span>
