</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='607070' id='t-607070'>So what this new research tells us, then,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='608975' id='t-608975'>is that the one thing that all of you</span>
