<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='612710' id='t-612710'>that even Galen understood about sleep,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615363' id='t-615363'>that it refreshes and clears the mind,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618434' id='t-618434'>may actually be a big part</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='619975' id='t-619975'>of what sleep is all about.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622292' id='t-622292'>See, you and I, we go to sleep</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='623810' id='t-623810'>every single night,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625543' id='t-625543'>but our brains, they never rest.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628546' id='t-628546'>While our body is still</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='630380' id='t-630380'>and our mind is off walking in dreams somewhere,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='633451' id='t-633451'>the elegant machinery of the brain</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635127' id='t-635127'>is quietly hard at work</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637107' id='t-637107'>cleaning and maintaining</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639300' id='t-639300'>this unimaginably complex machine.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='642135' id='t-642135'>Like our housework,</span>
