<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='645925' id='t-645925'>but it's also important.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='648180' id='t-648180'>In your house, if you stop cleaning your kitchen</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='650583' id='t-650583'>for a month,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='652491' id='t-652491'>your home will become completely unlivable</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654930' id='t-654930'>very quickly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656537' id='t-656537'>But in the brain, the consequences</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658625' id='t-658625'>of falling behind may be much greater</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='661556' id='t-661556'>than the embarrassment of dirty countertops,</span>
