<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678682' id='t-678682'>may be critical for preventing and treating</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='681675' id='t-681675'>diseases of the mind tomorrow.</span>
</span>
</p>
